OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778529954
OL,3,CDate revealed for the publication of
OL,4,CNottingham's maternity review
OL,6,FThe date for the publication of
OL,7,FNottingham's maternity review has been
OL,8,Fannounced as June 24.
OL,10,FAt a family meeting in the city this
OL,11,Fweekend, the review's chair Donna
OL,12,FOckenden said confirmed she'd play a
OL,13,Frole in overseeing the improvements
OL,14,Fmade by the trust after the report is
OL,15,Fpublished.
OL,17,FMembers of Nottingham University
OL,18,FHospitals board, who were invited by
OL,19,Ffamilies to attend, said the trust
OL,20,Fwill not "breathe a sigh of relief and
OL,21,Fmove on" once the report is out.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
