OL,3,CDate revealed for the publication of
OL,4,CNottingham's maternity review
OL,6,FIt's the largest ever inquiry into a
OL,7,Fsingle service in the history of the
OL,8,FNHS, with around 2,500 families
OL,9,Finvolved.
OL,11,FFour family sessions will follow the
OL,12,Freview publication on Thursday, June
OL,13,F25 and Friday June 26. It's an
OL,14,Fopportunity for families to meet with
OL,15,FDonna Ockenden in a small group and
OL,16,Fask questions.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
