PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778529954
OL,3,CDate revealed for the publication of
OL,4,CNottingham's maternity review
OL,6,FAll families will receive an
OL,7,Findividual report from the review
OL,8,Fteam. Donna Ockenden told families it
OL,9,Fwould be "based entirely on what
OL,10,Fhappened to them" and not be "cut and
OL,11,Fpaste".
OL,13,FFamily feedback sessions will continue
OL,14,Funtil November. Psychological services
OL,15,Fwill also be accessible after the
OL,16,Freview.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
