OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778529954
OL,3,CDate revealed for the publication of
OL,4,CNottingham's maternity review
OL,6,FMembers of the Nottingham University
OL,7,FHospitals Trust board, including Chief
OL,8,FExecutive Anthony May, attended the
OL,9,Ffamily meeting on Saturday at the
OL,10,Ffamilies' request for the first time.
OL,12,FHe said NUH "will not breathe a sigh
OL,13,Fof relief and move on" after the
OL,14,Freport's publication and Donna
OL,15,FOckenden and her team leave
OL,16,FNottingham. He said the review's
OL,17,Fpublication would be a "watershed
OL,18,Fmoment."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
