OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778529954
OL,3,CDate revealed for the publication of
OL,4,CNottingham's maternity review
OL,6,FDonna Ockenden confirmed to families
OL,7,Fshe would have a role in overseeing
OL,8,Fthe improvements post-review.
OL,10,F"It'll be part-time of course but my
OL,11,Finvolvement is likely to be for maybe
OL,12,Ftwo years. I think that provides
OL,13,Fcontinuity for the trust.
OL,15,F"You heard Anthony May today say the
OL,16,Fimportance of continuing the
OL,17,Frelationship that they've worked so
OL,18,Fhard to build with me and my team and
OL,19,Ffamilies.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
